bb2","tid":41313,"uid":57186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T20:11:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>晚晚最早4點最遲6，7點訓<br />\n最早都一兩點先起身<br />\n餐餐出街食<br />\n晚晚食宵夜<br />\n除左打完波極少飲水<br />\n一日都飲唔到一杯<br />\n淨係會買野飲/食飯飲凍檸茶<br />\n唯一好d係一星期會做幾日運動<br />\n諗到再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n晚晚最早5點,最遲7,8點訓<br />\n最早都兩,三點先起身<br />\n50%出街食 50% 食致癌物(腸仔,火腿,牛餐肉)+垃圾公仔面<br />\n咁晏先訓,食宵夜是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我有時會落樓食埋早餐tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過飲水就好過你,正正常常咁,一日都有4,5杯<br />\n<br />\n 唯一好d係一星期會做幾日運動 &lt;--一樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知幾時中癌"},{"pid":"e663b8b704dddb487225e7e966f51c729e29fb81","tid":41313,"uid":33555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T20:17:00.000Z","msg":"每日都等到有太陽先訓得著<br />\n起身時間唔定時<br />\n零運動<br />\n日日食街外野<br />\n飲紙包or罐裝野多過飲水<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca15d46a06253e50b63af688a3300362ef12488","tid":41313,"uid":8232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T20:17:15.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣但冇做運動冇食宵夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623d244e93ad3956d4d6b3d53864df9fdbe3ea7a","tid":41313,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T20:24:14.000Z","msg":"除左做運動全部中晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2a359c5930107132d9b8fbc3b891ccce99e300","tid":41313,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T22:03:57.000Z","msg":"夜瞓十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dec80d2cbd401e33ca27839112cd0a25609f195","tid":41313,"uid":61418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T22:19:13